category: Libs
requires: cygwin
external-source: pcsc-lite
sdesc: "Middleware to access a smart card using SCard API (runtime)"
ldesc: "The purpose of PCSC Lite is to provide a Windows(R) SCard interface in
a very small form factor for communicating to smart cards and readers. PCSC
Lite can be compiled directly to a desired reader driver or can be used to
dynamically allocate/deallocate reader drivers at runtime (default)."
